The paper deals with improving OCR accuracy, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The methods used in the paper involve pretraining and active learning, which are techniques commonly used in deep learning (cs.DL). The paper also mentions using cross fold training and voting, which are techniques used in machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with text recognition on early printed books, which is a task related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
